OL,3,CAlmost 170,000 retail employees lost
OL,4,Ctheir jobs in 2024, figures reveal
OL,6,FIt is the highest annual reading since
OL,7,Fmore than 200,000 jobs were lost in
OL,8,F2020 in the aftermath of the Covid-19
OL,9,Fpandemic, which forced retailers to
OL,10,Fshut their stores during lockdowns.
OL,12,FThe centre said 38 major retailers
OL,13,Fwent into administration in 2024,
OL,14,Fincluding household names such as
OL,15,FLloyds Pharmacy, Homebase, The Body
OL,16,FShop, Carpetright and Ted Baker.
